{
  "stem": "19807.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She found that in the Sephardic tradition, when the woman is pregnant, they treat her like a queen.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So she stayed pregnant most of her life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "She had 13 children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And very fortunately, they did not die at birth.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So they did not die.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Of all the children, I remember my father speaking of one of his favorite sisters that passed away, and how he would go to temple and pray for her while she was sick.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he became very bitter after he-- he lost that sister.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I remember that, the-- telling me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Going back to the-- to the-- it was called in-- in Bulgarian, [BULGARIAN].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So when my mother would see it, they would shudder, because they were always afraid maybe some of their friends would be.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Because they were friends and they were liberal.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And some of them, they're socialist.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And some of them were also at that time, with-- with other parties, very liberal.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And she hated to see anyone-- any harm come to anyone.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "She was a very, very fine, fine, saintly woman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Extremely intelligent.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But then when my father-- he was very young.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He was handsome.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And the whole family on-- on my father's side are dark, Mediterranean-type.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Whereby-- I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It's in the same country.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But on my mother's side, they all were very fair.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "My mother had practically blond hair, very fair hair, and fair, white skin, like-- like ivory.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And all my uncles, the same way.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And here, you have the contradiction of my father, dark, my mother, very light.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "My brother looks and has the skin of my mother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And I have the skin of my father.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father political affiliation, primarily affiliated with Jewish causes.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
